<emphasis id="175C2F66B04DA77085A81400B2C4F660" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="207">Y.M. Shui et al. 15105</emphasis>
(KUN); at the same county, in the limestone seasonal forests, alt. 1000-1200 m, with fruits of last year, 28 March 2002, 
<emphasis id="C3B2898A062A190F1258350630530C0A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="207">Y.M. Shui et al. 20595</emphasis>
