<emphasis id="B1AB91F534A3FFD6BF5FC07B9EBC8BA8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="207">Y.M. Shui et al. s.n.</emphasis>
(KUN); at the same county, in the limestone evergreen broad-leaved forests, alt. 794 m, 11 November 2006, 
<emphasis id="FF455714196B41C3E089E5D6F664B03D" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="207">Y.M. Shui et al. 16118</emphasis>
